<main role=""main"" class=""pb-3"">
   <h2> What is Totally Reel? </h2>
   <p>
      Totally Reel Movie Reviews is the best platform around to leave reviews and ratings for your favorite Reel Movies! All you need is an email to register for a TRMR account
      to begin sharing your thoughts and seeing what other Totally Reel Reviewers have to say.
   </p>
   <h2> Rules </h2>
   <p>
      We DO have some guidelines when it comes to posting reviews on our site. Failure to comply with these rules can result in your review being removed, and repeat offenders
      may find their reviewing priviledges taken away. 
   </p>
   <ol>
   <li> No posting irrelevant information. </li>
   <p> We want users to be able to read reviews and commentary about films without sifting through unrelated comments! Please refrain from discussing topics 
      that aren't related to the film that the review or comment is for. 
   </p>
   <li> No posting comments recommending or reviewing other movies </li>
   <p> This goes in hand with t");
            WriteLiteral(@"he previous rule. Please keep comments relevant, and don't talk about other films. It is okay to mention other movies as a comparison or to mention 
      a prequel or sequel, but please refrain from recommending or reviewing another movie, and save that content for the appropriate page for that film. 
   </p>
   <li> No using racial slurs, discrimitory language, or hate speech </li>
   <p> Everyone is allowed to use our site, and we want all of our users to feel safe and free to discuss movies they enjoy. While Totally Reel values free speech, we also acknowledge
      the importance of taking a stand against behavior that we deem inappropriate. In addition, in the spirit of keeping our review sections relevant, we do not see how using 
      derogatory language would be important to a movie review. Thus, please refrain from such behavior.
   </p>
   <li> No over posting reviews on a single movie page, except to reply to others </li>
   <p> We don't want our comment sections flooded with tons of reviews writ");
