      clarify or mention something you forgot, please wait an appropriate amount of time before writing another review. It is okay, however, to reply to other comments or respond to others as often as you 
      like! <em style=""color:red;"">Please refrain from leaving a score on any followup comments on movie pages!</em>
   </p>
   <li> Be as unbiased as possible in your reviews </li>
   <p>It is inevitable that your personal opinion will influence your review for a movie, even for professional movie critics. However, try your best to remove your 
